Ted Raimi https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ted_Raimi 0 Theodore Raimi (born December 14, 1965) is an American actor, director, comedian, and writer perhaps best known for his role as Joxer the Mighty in Xena: Warrior Princess/Hercules: The Legendary Journeys. Raimi plays Ted Hoffman in his brother Sam Raimi's Spider-Man trilogy.
